"13:41:9" : {s: 13, a: 41, w: 9, r: "اله", t: "وَٱللَّهُ", l: "ٱللَّه", lc: 2811, tl: "wal-lahu", lb: "আল্লাহ",e: "And Allah", b: "অথচ আল্লাহ", i: "dan Allah", f: 239, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things."},
